                  "type": "Annotation",
                  "motivation": "commenting",
                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p>had not been allowed to have come<lb/> or your advice counsel at\n                                        this<lb/> moment would have so beneficial<lb/> your\n                                        consolation so healing to [?]<lb/> wounded spirits, nay to\n                                        the preservation<lb/> of our future prosperity – Your\n                                        administration [?] have a great deal to answer for in<lb/>\n                                        their indifference to their unfortunate Brethren<lb/> their\n                                        sworn religion, they have shown<lb/> thereby favourable to\n                                        our opponents by<lb/> their refusal have encouraged them\n                                        made<lb/> it apparent that your congregation were\n                                        favourable<lb/> [?] views – My feeling will not allow<lb/>\n                                        me to carry this better to any extent I<lb/> therefore pray\n                                        your continuance of health<lb/> life [?] me to be your\n                                        friend</p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(4)\">\n                                        <persName role=\"author\">Samuel Hart Sen.</persName>\n                              </p>\n                              <p>Please send <persName>Mr. Rosenfeldt</persName> occident by\n                                        mail</p>\n                              <p>\n                                        <persName>I.C. Levy</persName>\n                                        <persName>Rev Dr Curtis</persName>\n                              </p>\n                              <p>Discontinue</p>\n                              <p>I have had several [?] of the Conciliator from\n                                                  <placeName>England</placeName>, cost 8 shillings\n                                        Sherl[?] Lander [?]<lb/> 42.67 I dont know your agent but if\n                                        all the books<lb/> he sends you are in the same proportion.\n                                        [?] are dear enough –</p>"
                  },
